--------------

Background:

Stuff mostly done using : http://linux-sunxi.org/Building_on_Debian

--------------

Usage:

If you need to create armhf kernel packages using cross-compiling, please use
the following patch :

Here is a sample make-kpkg that can be used for such build:
$ make-kpkg --arch armhf --arch-in-name --revision 1 --append-to-version sunxi --cross_compile arm-linux-gnueabihf- --rootcmd fakeroot --zimage kernel_headers kernel_image kernel_source kernel_doc

